title: Week 5 Recap: Toney, Chase, Brady and More! (10/10 Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We're recapping a wild Week 5 that featured some fantastic NFL finishes and high-scoring Fantasy matchups. Our biggest winner is Kadarius Toney (2:00). Our biggest loser is Odell Beckham (4:00). And we'll talk about the biggest injuries (5:45) including all of the Giants who left Sunday's game ... More winners (10:00) like Amon-Ra St. Brown and Myles Gaskin and losers (18:30) like Miles Sanders and T.J. Hockenson. Then we do some rest of season rankings (26:40): Ja'Marr Chase or Keenan Allen? Deebo Samuel or Darrell Henderson? Justin Fields or Trey Lance (29:30)? Allen Robinson or ANYONE (32:00)!? ... Recapping all of the games with our Fantasy thoughts (36:30) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
